messages.message: We are thrilled to announce that Masaiverse is coming to Lucknow, Uttar Pradesh on June 11th!This is an exciting opportunity for us to bring our community together and celebrate our shared passion for innovation, creativity, and skills.To find out more about the event and to register your interest, please fill out the form - https://lu.ma/masaiverseUP We can't wait to see you all there and to share this amazing experience with you.Best regards, Masaiverse Team
